data.description: You'll absolutely love this updated town house located in York County near military installations (Fort Eustis and Naval Weapons Station) and York County schools!  Paint, appliances (to include washer and dryer) and carpet were updated/installed less than 3 years ago. Stainless steel appliances and Corian countertops round out this open floor plan!  The upstairs has a great layout with 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths and washer and dryer (no hauling laundry up and down the stairs!). Fenced in back yard area is perfect for outdoor entertaining and also provides privacy.  Conveniently located near the pool and club house.  Enjoy the local area which is just a short drive to historic Yorktown battlefields with walking and biking trails, restaurants, shopping and beaches!  A MUST SEE!
